Package FOMS.branch_manager

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IOpenCloseBranch
    The IOpenCloseBranch interface defines the contract for classes that handle opening and closing branches.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AllBranch
    The AllBranch class provides methods related to retrieving branch IDs.
    AOpenCloseBranch
    The AOpenCloseBranch class is an abstract class that provides common methods for reading and writing branch information to a text file.
    Branch
    The Branch class represents a branch in the FOMS system.
    BranchQuotaManager
    The BranchQuotaManager class manages branch quotas for staff members.
    CloseBranch
    The CloseBranch class is responsible for closing a branch.
    DisplayManagerBranchStaff
    The DisplayManagerBranchStaff class provides methods to display details of staff members managed by a branch manager.
    OpenBranch
    The OpenBranch class is responsible for opening a new branch and saving its details.
    OpenCloseBranchPage
    The OpenCloseBranchPage class provides functionality to open or close a branch.
    ReadBranchList
    The ReadBranchList class provides functionality to read a list of branches from a file.
    Restaurant
    The Restaurant class represents a restaurant with branches, staff, and menu items.
